<div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto py-12 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
  <div class="text-center mb-12">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-stone-900 sm:text-4xl">
      The Sacred Ceremony & Application
    </h2>
    <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-stone-500 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      Râpé is an ancient ceremonial practice rooted in ancestral healing traditions. Approach it with respect, intention, and a focused state of mind.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-3">
    <div class="bg-stone-50 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-stone-100 flex flex-col justify-between">
      <div>
        <div class="text-stone-500 font-mono text-sm mb-4">STEP 01</div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-stone-900 mb-2">Prepare Intention</h3>
        <p class="text-stone-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
          Sit comfortably with your back straight to allow energy to flow. Pour a pea-sized amount of powder into your non-dominant palm, set your intention, and bring the pipe to your forehead and heart to express gratitude.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-stone-50 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-stone-100 flex flex-col justify-between">
      <div>
        <div class="text-stone-500 font-mono text-sm mb-4">STEP 02</div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-stone-900 mb-2">The Application</h3>
        <p class="text-stone-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
          Inhale deeply and hold your breath. Place the long end of the kuripe pipe in your nostril (or use a tepi for serving another person) and blow the powder in. Inhale and breathe gently through your mouth.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-stone-50 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-stone-100 flex flex-col justify-between">
      <div>
        <div class="text-stone-500 font-mono text-sm mb-4">STEP 03</div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-stone-900 mb-2">Cleanse & Integrate</h3>
        <p class="text-stone-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
          Immediately repeat with the second nostril to maintain balance. The active substances absorb within 10-15 minutes. Remain in a calm environment, focus on the warmth and gratitude, and allow integration.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="mt-8 bg-amber-50/50 border border-amber-200/60 p-5 rounded-2xl text-stone-700 text-xs leading-relaxed max-w-3xl mx-auto">
    <span class="font-semibold text-amber-800">Important Disclaimer:</span> The above description is provided for historical, cultural and educational purposes only. We expressly offer our Râpé for incense and ritual burning purposes only. The use and application of our products is solely at the customer's decision, responsibility, and risk.
  </div>
</div>
